ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ

- Make the main Workbench window backdrop:

	WBAttack DOBACKDROP
	WBAttack ON

- Make the main Workbench window normal:

	WBAttack NOBACKDROP
	WBAttack OFF

- Switch the backdrop mode of the main Workbench window:

	WBAttack SWITCH


@ENDNODE

